node.text:
Here is the after movie of STANCENATION JAPAN held at Kirara Expo Memorial Park in Yamaguchi.

This was our first time hosting the event in Yamaguchi! Thank you to everyone who participated!

Details will be available in upcoming issues of Geibunsha magazine as well as our site. You can also watch the live broadcast of the day's events on the “Stance JP Channel” on YouTube.

Event Date: November 8th 2020
Location: KIRARA EXPO MEMORIAL PARK (yamaguchi)
Vendors: 45
Entry Cars : 518 (1523 registered!)
Organizer: stancenation.com
Sponsored magazines:
Stance magazine,CUSTOM CAR,eS4,NostalgicSPEED,HACHIMARU HERO,VIP CAR mobile
